          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Right to Timely Rehearings at FERC Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill revises the rehearing process for petitioners aggrieved by an order issued by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC) with respect to licensing for projects under the Federal Power Act. Specifically, the bill revises the process to speed up the time line for FERC to respond to requests for rehearing orders.</p>]]>
        </text>
